WEBVTT

00:11:59.292 --> 00:12:02.736
the number one question facing us

00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:07.407
is how not to allow
ourselves to be manipulated

00:12:07.431 --> 00:12:10.237
by those who control the data.

00:12:11.387 --> 00:12:15.493
The enemies of liberal democracy,
they have a method.

00:12:15.919 --> 00:12:18.291
They hack our feelings.

00:12:18.315 --> 00:12:20.767
Not our emails, not our bank accounts --

00:12:20.791 --> 00:12:25.998
they hack our feelings of fear
and hate and vanity,

00:12:26.022 --> 00:12:28.450
and then use these feelings

00:12:28.474 --> 00:12:32.426
to polarize and destroy
democracy from within.